      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas wehl no Baësus Leetahm atleek/ un ko wiſch irr darrijs/ un winna Spehks/ tas irr rakſthts to Israëta Kehnizu Laiku-Grahmata."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Baësus afs migge ar fa weem Tehweem / un tappe Tirzâ aprakts/ un winna Dehls Ellus tappe par Kehnizu winna Weetâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir ta KUNGA Wahrdz notikke zaur to Praweetu Jeü/ Ananns Dehlu/ prett Baësu un winna Namnu/ wiſa Zauna pehz/ ko wiſch irr darrijs preeſch ta KUNGA Azzim/ winnu ar fatvu Rohkas Darhu apkaitina dams/ un ta patt buhdams/ ka Jerobeama Namś/ un ka wiſch to paſchu bij kawis."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Iwideſmitâ festâ Gaddâ ta Kehnizu no Juhda/ tappe Ellus Baësus Dehls par Kehnizu pahr Ifraëlu Tirzâ/ (un waldja) diwi Gaddus."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Kalps Simrus"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "tas Wirfneeks pahr to weenit Puſſi to Rattu Pulku/ darrija weenit Derribu prett winnu. Kad wiſch Tirzâ bija labbi der dams eekſch Arza ta Aumeistera Namna/ Tirzâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sinrus nahze eekſcha/ un kaue to/ un nokawe to divi definitis ſeptitâ Gaddâ ta Keh nitra no Juhda/ un tas tappe par Kehniza winna Weetâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad wiſch nu waldja/ un us tawn Krehſtu tehdeja/ tad kaue wiſch wiſu Baësus Nam mu/ wiſch ne atlizzinaja ne weenu/ kas pee Seenas meeſu/ nedg winna Affinn-Raddus/ nedg winna Draugus."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta isdeldeja Simrus wiſu Baësus Namnu pehz ta KUNGA Wahrdzu/ ko wiſch prett Baësu bij runnajs zaur to Praweetu Jen."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſu Baësus Grehku deht/ un Ellus winna Dehla Grehku deht/ ko tee bij darrijschi/ un Israëlu bij darrijschi grehkoht/ apkaitinadami to KUNGU Isra eka Deewu ar sawahm Negantibahm."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas wehl no Ellus Leetahm atleek/ un wiſs/ ko wiſch darrijs/ tas irr rakſthts to Israëta Kehnizu Laiku-Grah mata."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Diwideſmitâ ſeptitâGaddâ Afkus ta Kehnizu no Juhda/ tappe Simrus par Kehnizu pahr Juhdu/ (un waldja) ſeptins Deenas Tirzâ/ un tee ſaudis Sſſſ bij"
    }
  ],
